        <name>ToEquation</name>
        <qualifiedname>Baruah.MathsEngine.LogicalNode.ToEquation</qualifiedname>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Builds a parenthesized ternary equation string representing this logical node and its comparison entries. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="return"><para>A string containing a parenthesized ternary expression of the form &quot;(&lt;comparison-chain&gt; ? &lt;trueExpression&gt; : &lt;falseExpression&gt;)&quot;. Each comparison is rendered as &quot;A Symbol B&quot; and comparisons are joined using their logical operator symbols. Null child expressions or operators are rendered as &quot;0&quot; or &quot;?&quot; respectively. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
